title: Customer Service Interview
Application Type: I applied through a recruiter. The process took 12 months. I interviewed at Job Squad (Helsinki, Southern Finland) in Apr 2022
Interview Descriptions: This is a really professional and helpful recruiting company. Their recruiters keep in touch regularly on the relevant job opportunities, book screening calls by email communication, provide full information on at least two job opportunities during one screening call, are vividly focused on job seekers. My every and each communication with their recruiters has been a step forward in my employment development.
Interview Questions: What jobs are you interested in?
